PRIVACY POLICY
Vadim Shilov pr Beograd / Vadim Shilov pr Racunarsko programiranje Beograd (“we,” “us,” or “our”) is a mobile application development company registered in the Republic of Serbia. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share personal information through our mobile applications (“Apps”) and outlines your rights regarding that information.
By using our Apps, you agree to this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please discontinue use of our Apps.
Company Information
Soler Proprietor name: Vadim Shilov pr Beograd / Vadim Shilov pr Racunarsko programiranje Beograd
Registration Number: 67687949
Tax ID: 114576744
Address: Jurija Gagarina 231, Belgrade, 11073, Republic of Serbia
Data Collection and Usage
We collect and process personal data for the purpose of enhancing your user experience and improving our Apps. The data we collect includes, but is not limited to:
Usage statistics
Device information
Application installation sources
In-app activities
Service Providers
We use the following tools and services for data collection and analysis:
1. Google Analytics: To gather anonymized data about user interactions with the App to improve its functionality and content.
2. Google Ads: To manage advertising campaigns and understand user acquisition metrics.
These tools comply with global privacy regulations, and we ensure your data is handled securely.
Compliance with GDPR and Other Regulations
As a company distributing Apps within the European Union, we comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). We adhere to the following principles:
Collecting data only for authorized purposes.
Ensuring data accuracy and minimizing exposure.
Implementing robust security measures, including encryption.
Deleting user data upon consent withdrawal or the end of a service agreement.
Your Rights
You have the right to:
Access the personal data we hold about you.
Request correction or deletion of your data.
Withdraw your consent to data processing.
To exercise your rights, contact us at: support@kidify.games
Data Retention
We retain user data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Data will be erased in the following situations:
Upon user request.
At the end of a service or agreement.
Data Security
We implement advanced security measures to protect your data, including encryption, secure storage, and breach notification protocols. In case of a data breach, we will:
Notify regulatory authorities within 72 hours.
Inform affected users promptly.
Provide details of the breach and recommended actions.
Changes to This Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy as necessary. Significant changes will be communicated through our Apps or other appropriate channels. Continued use of our Apps after updates constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.
